        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2011-05-13 15:11:44.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 9: (1 inline comment)\n\nI think that for this to be pushed the JIRA needs to specify something about the target SLES 11. Without that information it's not really possible to verify the change has captured what's required.\n\nFor example why change to inkernel ofed, I can imagine why but details in the JIRA would mean I'd know why.\n\nI'll remain neutral on whether this if good to go on that front, but prefer it not landed because of the apparent extra and unused function.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 9
    },
